  • public class Overlap2DMapLoader
extends com.badlogic.gdx.assets.loaders.AsynchronousAssetLoader<Overlap2DMapSettings,Overlap2DMapLoader.Parameters>
    Loads and Overlap2D Scene to a WKWorld and returns a setting file.
    Paths should be given as internal strings. The TextureAtlas will be loaded if it hasn't already.
